      <body>
         <div xml:lang="la">
            <p n="a#1" xml:space="preserve">Anno mcdxxiiii die beatorum Tiburcii et Valeriani in <placeName>capitulo generali</placeName>
      ita ordinatum et statutum, quod qualibet sexta feria in <placeName>capitulo</placeName>
      intimentur anniversaria sequentis ebdomade et dominica sequenti de
        <placeName>ambone</placeName> populo intimentur. ♦</p>
            <p n="a#2" xml:space="preserve"><app><lem>Item quilibet <placeName>canonicus residens</placeName> in
            <placeName>civitate</placeName> existens pro qualibet horarum sive misse matutinorum et
          vesperarum, si se absentaverat, solvat i solidum Lubicensem pro pena in summis
          festis</lem><rdg wit="#A">Overstreget i A</rdg></app>. ♦</p>
            <p n="a#3" xml:space="preserve">Item quilibet canonicus residens in civitate existens, si absens fuerit in summis festis,
      missis, vesperis et matutinis, pro qualibet istarum horarum solvat i solidum Lubicensem
      usualis monete pro pena, quem si infra octo dies, postquam requisitus fuerit, non solverit, <app><lem>careat</lem><rdg wit="#A">Herefter overstreget <q>usum</q>; i marginen en pegende hånd, A</rdg></app> distribucione, donec solvat. ♦</p>
            <p n="a#4" xml:space="preserve">Similiter et qui absens fuerit a processionibus in summis festis et dominicis diebus inter
      pascha et festum corporis Christi, solvat solidum Lubicensem pro pena eadem.</p>
            <p n="a#5" xml:space="preserve">Item quilibet canonicus residens extra civitatem Ripensem existens in summis festis, solvat
        iiii<hi rend="sup">or</hi> solidos Lubicenses in pena pro quolibet festo ut supra, nisi <app><lem>petita</lem><rdg wit="#A">Herforinden overstreget <q>petita</q>, A</rdg></app> licencia a cantore vel duobus senioribus canonicis et optenta.</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:lang="da">
            <p n="b#1" xml:space="preserve">I perioden frem til 30. juni 2021 vil redaktionen udelukkende udarbejde tekster.</p>
